{"tid":2317311,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店「桔梗」今午收警通知再搜查後告吹　晚市如常","createTime":"2020-12-08T12:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T13:06:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb56be3ec24c18229261f50931fd11404dc923a","tid":2317311,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"旺角「黃店」桔梗早前被大批警員搜查近 3 小時，警方指在餐廳搜出伸縮棍、盾牌、頭盔、防毒面具等物品，兩名負責人被捕。桔梗今午在社交媒體表示，收到警方致電通知，預約今日下午 5 時會持搜令再到餐廳搜查，預計會撿走閉路電視。<br />\n<br />\n到下午 5 時，大批記者在餐廳外守候，部份餐廳員工都坐下停止工作。但一直未見有警員到場搜證。餐廳負責人 6 時許表示，剛收到警方通知指不會在今日到場。餐廳的晚市如常營業，陸續見到有市民光顧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/130712955_3711945648891028_3634576153054509975_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=LPtFVEuplsYAX9-S2k_&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=cff96f3d504d7e170e59cc19345baa24&amp;oe=5FF65D01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F130712955_3711945648891028_3634576153054509975_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DLPtFVEuplsYAX9-S2k_%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dcff96f3d504d7e170e59cc19345baa24%26oe%3D5FF65D01&h=0065d042&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae3d80fafd5c434a03995211760abe38df371231","tid":2317311,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a682e693bd7266e24739274474bae368ec8a5a","tid":2317311,"uid":271894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"去左好鄰舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"b55b4056cdfba3727affba77af11ba79801d